{
  "id": "61f0dc83fd77a30020eda324",
  "title": "(6.2.6) Summary of verbalization",
  "created": 1643175121,
  "updated": 1643178152,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61f0dc83fd77a30020eda324",
      "text": "(6.2.6) Summary of verbalization",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175121,
      "updated": 1643178152
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0dcd1aff09e00009e4639",
      "text": "In this section, as a part of the method of [gathering information], we explained with emphasis on how to retrieve information that already exists among you and others. *39",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175121,
      "updated": 1643177931
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e7c1aff09e00008b69b9",
      "text": "Finally, let's review.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643177921,
      "updated": 1643177921
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0dcd1aff09e00009e463a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175121,
      "updated": 1643175121
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0dd02aff09e00004f6f76",
      "text": "I collected the mention about the [iceberg model].",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175170,
      "updated": 1643175311
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0dd5caff09e00004f6f78",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/4ac065b23d02ea969c279bd632a0a1c4]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175261,
      "updated": 1643175273
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0dd68aff09e00004f6f79",
      "text": "[Overall picture of the iceberg model]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175273,
      "updated": 1643175277
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0dd5caff09e00004f6f77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175260,
      "updated": 1643175260
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e008aff09e0000569a96",
      "text": "It is important to pay attention to what have not been words yet.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643175944,
      "updated": 1643176490
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e229aff09e0000569a97",
      "text": "For example, body sensation, experience and discomfort. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176490,
      "updated": 1643176490
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e229aff09e0000569a99",
      "text": "When trying to make words, it often happens to be in the form of a parable or a metaphor.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176490,
      "updated": 1643176493
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e229aff09e0000569a9a",
      "text": "The words that just came out may not be conveyed to people without explanation.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176490,
      "updated": 1643176493
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e229aff09e0000569a9b",
      "text": "But you do not have to be afraid of. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176490,
      "updated": 1643176493
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e229aff09e0000569a9c",
      "text": "It is good to take your thought out of yourself first, write it down and keep it from disappearing, and then improve it to a form that is conveyed to other people.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176490,
      "updated": 1643176490
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e229aff09e0000569a9d",
      "text": "Even if it is written in a language only to you, the words work as handles, and those make you easier to operate your thought.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176490,
      "updated": 1643176490
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e229aff09e0000569a9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176490,
      "updated": 1643176490
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e230aff09e0000569a9f",
      "text": "On the other hand, as in the example of \"[voice of birds]\", it is also common that the the handle is disconnected from a concrete experience. In that case, you need to go down to a physical sensation or an experience and reconnect it with the [handle]. The purpose here is to connect \"what is not verbalized yet inside of you\" and \"the handle as words\". ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643176496,
      "updated": 1643177307
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e52baff09e0000569aa0",
      "text": "Making words without the connection is useless. It is like a [rootless grass]. It will die soon.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643177260,
      "updated": 1643177265
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e52baff09e0000569aa1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643177260,
      "updated": 1643177260
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e7ceaff09e00008b69ba",
      "text": "*39:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643177935,
      "updated": 1643177937
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e7d1aff09e00008b69bc",
      "text": "I have chosen \"[verbalization]\" as a relatively easy to understand word. However, there are many ways of extracting information, not limited to language, such as the arrangement of cards, pictures, and gestures. By using [Ikujiro Nonaka]'s term, \"[externalization]\" is more appropriate.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643177937,
      "updated": 1643178091
    },
    {
      "id": "61f0e831aff09e00008b69bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1643178034,
      "updated": 1643178034
    },
